pect the rights of all individuals our only bias is toward our clients to assist them in all of lifes financial events what wall street does and says has no bearing on us we work for our clients and no one else we believe… the american dream is alive and well that all americans benefit from setting financial goals developing a written plan and working with a partner toward the achievement of those goals that all investment strategies work some of the time and that no investment strategy works all of the time our fiduciary obligation is to our client and not wall street the fear of the future and the greed of consumerism are the roadblocks to financial independence for all americans in the human spirit and free will in the power of partnership firmhistory ourstory advantage ofindependence local and nationalresources firm historylike you our cofounders david  stacy hefty had their own american dream after working for a large national investment firm and learning the ins and outs of the brokerage world david  stacy dreamt of a different way of helping americans work towards achieving their financial goals they dreamt of a team of diverse financial professionals working together and collaborating with clients and other trusted advisors such as attorneys bankers and tax accountants they dreamt of a long term relationship where the advice given was objective by the summer of  this dream became a reality when they left their jobs and their brokerage firm’s clients and moved three hours north to start over from scratch with nothing but their dream and each other’s support the firm has achieved several notable accolades over the years but this has been the result of our team living out our belief statements our storyhefty wealth partners is a knowledgeable community of financial professionals who believe communication education honesty and integrity are the four pillars of every successful relationship working as a team our professionals simplify the demands of wealth helping to manage all aspects of your financial life so you can spend more time on other important priorities like family or your business we serve accomplished individuals families businesses trusts estates corporations and foundations seeking a committed partner to help identify and work toward achieving individual financial goals advantage of independencewe believe our fiduciary obligation is to our client and not wall street our independence helps provide the confidence you seek to pursue financial success on your terms at hefty wealth partners we recognize the importance of our responsibility to provide you with prudent investment management and objective advice as independent advisors we focus solely on serving your needs and acting in your best interest at all times this provides you with the confidence you seek to pursue financial success on your terms as an independent registered investment advisory ria firm we have no obligations to investment product manufacturers and no crosssell quotas or homeoffice directives that may lead to conflicts of interest instead we spend our time developing customized strategies for the unique challenges you face local and national resourceshefty wealth partners provides you access to the resources information and experience you require to pursue your goals with confidence once we know where you want to go we put your money and our extensive resources to work to help get you there our commitment to communication and education ensures you remain informed about economic events tax legislation financial market activity and other information that may impact your financial decisions our wealth partners are frequent guests and subject matter professionals for local and national print and broadcast media outlets all are highly experienced in interpreting complex financial data in an effort to help their clients and the public understand the potential outcomes of specific circumstances events and situations david hefty cfp® ceo wealth partner david hefty is the ceo and cofounder of hefty wealth partners david is a certified financial planner™ practitioner and a member of the financial planning association fpa angie lockwood cpa chief operations officer angie lockwood cpa is chief operations officer at hefty wealth partners she is responsible for overall operational efficiencies and technology integration as well as the execution of the firm’s strategic initiatives driving growth and profitability stacy hefty president wealth partner stacy hefty is the president and cofounder of hefty wealth partners she is also the former cohost with her husband david of “about your money” a live callin radio show that aired on wgl talk radio  for nearly three years edison byzyka cfa chief investment officer edison byzyka is the chief investment officer at hefty wealth partners he is responsible for managing all portfolio strategies across various risk objectives authoring the firm’s voice and leading all research and due diligence efforts                     check the background of investment professionals associated with this site on finras brokercheck doug lockwood mba cfp® branch president wealth partner doug lockwood brings extensive knowledge and experience to his role as branch president and wealth partner for hefty wealth partners with  years in the banking and financial services industry he is also a certified financial planner™ practitioner brian neal aams® financial advisor brian david neal is a wealth partner at hefty wealth partners having joined the firm in early  he works with clients to implement holistic individualized wealth plans and to help them work toward their financial goals by providing objective advice   close aboutservices▼legacy for lifeall servicesinvestment managementeducationfrontconnectlogin about  hefty wealth partners helping americans work toward their financial goals and dreams “our mission is to guide clients throughout life’s most important financial events with service and exper